Monsters are prowling through the farmlands of [[Tethyr]], people are starving, and the government is on the verge of collapse. But why? A 15-page adventure intended for four to six characters of levels 8-12. A party including a wizard and at least two warriors, is recommended; a ranger or any character with tracking proficiency would be useful. {{Dusup|38/A Blight On The Land}}
